{
  "stanzas": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "I have a Friend so precious,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "So very dear to me,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "He loves me with such tender love,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "He loves so faithfully;"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "I could not live apart form Him,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "I love to feel Him nigh,"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "And so we dwell together,"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "My Lord and I."
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Sometimes Iâ€™m faint and weary,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "He knows that I am weak,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "And as He bids me lean on Him,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "His help I gladly seek;"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "He leads me in the paths of light,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Beneath a sunny sky,"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "And so we walk together,"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "My Lord and I."
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "I tell Him all my sorrows,"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "I tell Him all my joys,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "I tell Him all that pleases me,"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "I tell Him what annoys;"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "He tells me what I ought to do,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "He tells me how to try,"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "And so we talk together,"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "My Lord and I."
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "He knows that I am longing"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "Some weary soul to win,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "And so He bids me go and speak"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "The loving word for Him;"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "He bids me tell His wondrous love,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "And why He came to die,"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "And so we work together,"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "My Lord and I."
        }
      ],
      "number": 4
    }
  ],
  "title": "My Lord and I"
}
